 {"id":"bd-2gkx.2","title":"WebSocket event loss telemetry + client alerts","description":"Add explicit event-loss notifications when WS ring buffers or throttlers drop messages. Emit counters/metrics, include last-drop timestamps, and publish a system:events channel message so UI can display a warning banner. Tests: unit tests for drop detection + serialization; integration tests verifying client receives loss notice; E2E test validates banner + logs with traces.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:18.703632899Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:18.703632899Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.2","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
